The paper discusses machine learning algorithms in medical imaging, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The focus of the paper is on methods that can learn with less supervision, such as semi-supervised learning (cs.LG), multiple instance learning (cs.AI), and transfer learning (cs.MM). Neural networks are also mentioned, which falls under the sub-category of neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
